data.description:
Nestled in the historic heart of Parkersburg, WV, at 1503 Washington Ave, this stately four-square home blends timeless architecture with modern amenities, offering an unrivaled living experience. As you approach this majestic residence, an expansive covered front porch welcomes you, complete with an outdoor ceiling fan, providing a serene haven for relaxation and entertainment. You will likely enjoy parades and other area events from this porch. 
This property boasts a 2-car detached garage and a convenient parking pad with alley access, ensuring ample parking and storage solutions. As you step inside, you are greeted by a grand foyer that sets the tone for the entire home. Original light fixtures, carefully preserved, adorn the foyer and dining room, casting a warm glow that highlights the home's historic charm and elegance. These exquisite details extend throughout areas of the home, creating a cohesive and inviting ambiance.

The kitchen has been thoughtfully updated. It features a new smart oven, and an oversized refrigerator, complemented by a dishwasher and disposal unit for utmost convenience. The new countertops provide ample preparation space, enhancing the kitchen's functionality and style. Adjacent to the kitchen, a half bath adds an extra layer of practicality to the ground floor layout.
Expanding on the living spaces, a large family room becomes a centerpiece for gatherings and relaxation. This versatile space is equipped with a pantry and coat closet for additional storage, while a gas fireplace adds warmth and ambiance to any occasion. The family room's generous dimensions accommodate various furniture arrangements, making it perfect for hosting cozy family nights.
This property represents a perfect blend of historical charm and modern conveniences, making it an exceptional home. With its prime location, extensive updates, and unique features this home is sure to go quickly.
